e </li></ul><b>Renal Impairment</b><ul><li>Cisplatin:<br>If CrCl 30-60 mL/min, reduce dose by 50%  <br>                                                                    If CrCl < 30 mL/min, do not use</li><li>Paclitaxel:<br>No dose reduction</li></ul>','Cisplatin : CDDP<br>Paclitaxel : Taxol');
