aminase > 10 upper normal limit or bilirubin > 7.5 mg/dL, do not use </li></ul><b>Renal Impairment</b><ul><li>Carboplatin:<br>Dosing based on AUC </li><li>Paclitaxel:<br>No dose reduction</li></ul>','Carboplatin : Paraplatin<br>Paclitaxel : Taxol');
